   Utah Scales E-mail Notification Service
   _______________________________________________________________________

    You may subscribe to receive an e-mail notification when new opinions
                   are posted to the Utah Courts' website.
   There is no charge for this service. To subscribe, simply fill out the
                 form below and click the subscribe button.
   _______________________________________________________________________

    Your Name:                     ____________________
    Your E-mail:                   ____________________

                  Select one or more of the options below:
                                [ ] Supreme Court Opinions
                              [ ] Court of Appeals Opinions
                 [ ] Court of Appeals Memorandum and Per Curiam Decisions
                                 Subscribe

   You will receive an e-mail confirmation when you have been successfully
                                   added.

